ght:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">、在校硕士研究生，金融、会计、财务相关专业，有一定金融专业知识背景，条件优秀的本科生亦可申请；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">、熟练</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\">WORD,EXCEL,PPT</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\">office</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">软件的运用，文笔好的优先考虑；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&#x4EFF;&#x5B8B;_GB2312\">3</span><span style=\"fon